==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Canceleer
<hw>Can"cel*eer</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>The turn
of a hawk upon the wing to recover herself, when she misses her aim in
the stoop.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The fierce and eager hawks, down thrilling from the skies,⟦br⟧
Make sundry <qex>canceliers</qex> ere they the fowl can reach.</q>
<rj><qau>Drayton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cancellarean</ent>⟦br⟧
